Name: Leech Seed
Effect: Single Target. Low Accuracy 1. Spend 1 Will Point to activate. At the end of each Round, Roll 2 Dice of Typeless Damage to the foe. User heals 1 HP for every damage dealt this way. Grass-Type Pokemon are immune to this Move.
Description: The user plants some seeds on the target, the seeds sprout and restore the user's health by absorbing the foe's vital energy.
